	(text "Translate IDE reset signals from 5v to 3.3v\nUsed to drive the Pi Pico Run (Pin 30)\n\nDue to the super cap if external power is applied\nwhilst the super cap is semi-charge, it can\ncause the Pico to not startup correctly. The\nreset line is designed to prevent this"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 71.374 114.046 0)
		(effects
